{"tid":2231982,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"寧贈洋人不予家奴! 支那疫苗被爆支那國內價格是出口價的20倍","createTime":"2020-10-06T05:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T07:56:31.000Z","uid":32511,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"059bfdc031d5ef1df58261acbea311a379b43bed","tid":2231982,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/CJJuAqK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FCJJuAqK.png&h=bf22799c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據中國媒體《鳳凰網》上個月底報導，中國預防武漢肺炎（新冠肺炎，COVID-19）的疫<br />\n苗定價已經出爐，1針300人民幣（約1,271台幣），2針600人民幣（約2,542台幣），並聲<br />\n稱目前已有10萬多名屬於高危險人群的民眾接種疫苗，無一例明顯不良反應，更無一人染<br />\n疫；然而該款疫苗卻被意外爆出，在國外只定價1針2美元（約13元人民幣）、2針4美元（<br />\n27元人民幣），價差超過20倍，令人咋舌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8X6KxFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8X6KxFA.jpg&h=f25d21cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-10-05/474934\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-10-05%2F474934&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZLwwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=215b3b7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-10-05/474934</a>"},{"pid":"6240cb65db0e4a4f682b58a825476d6213f1431b","tid":2231982,"uid":59684,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:25:19.000Z","msg":"中国有十四億人民，為國捐軀，不怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b6ae7051e36f288cb1d767c285f6cfd405438b","tid":2231982,"uid":47492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:25:19.000Z","msg":"支那有疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d3c97dfa872c3d08a36a0a2353b40774bd5901","tid":2231982,"uid":35919,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:26:45.000Z","msg":"唔開1萬都偷笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces